the norm. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill"><a class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!" href="https://www.propertyguru.com.my/property-guides/how-to-calculate-debt-service-ratio-dsr-12055?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Sharlife</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+3</span></span><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">PropertyGuru Malaysia</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+3</span></span><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">IQI Global</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+3</span></span></span></a></span></span></p></li><li data-start="2229" data-end="2425"><p data-start="2231" data-end="2425">Note: Banks differ in whether they use <strong data-start="2270" data-end="2300">gross income or net income</strong> (after EPF, SOCSO). And they may exclude certain income sources or debt obligations. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill"><a class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-